{"tid":659881,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人撐港式粵語","createTime":"2018-05-10T08:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T15:31:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20eba21387a5ebe2ef0aa985262e486ccc2a2027","tid":659881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180510/20385821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20385821&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6Gv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6f87ff22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F20385821&h=67bc0a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180510/20385821</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人撐港式粵語<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180510/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180510%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=df837713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我的日本朋友安野講一口流利的港式粵語（部分字音調失準），同為粵語，但港式粵語與廣州人的粵語在用詞及發音上都有些差異，安野說的是香港人的粵語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安野的港式粵語是在東京的語言學校學的，他說同學多數是娶了港女的日本男人，學好港式粵語是為了更好地與港女太太溝通。只有他，學港式粵語的目的是為了看港產片。他說無意中看過《無間道》之後就被港產片迷住了，為了更好地理解每一句台詞，的起心肝去學港式粵語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安野的港式粵語非常地道，他會聽、會說、會閱讀，還會書寫，寫出來的不是書面中文，而是地道粵語口語，比如他會發這種短訊給我，「你瞓咗覺未呀？有嘢想問你呀！你知唔知獎你暈係乜水？」<br />\n<br />\n連「獎你暈」都有興趣八，我就真係暈了！某次我貼了和安野晚餐的相片上FB，有網友讚安野是「小鮮肉」，安野回應說，「我唔係小鮮肉，我的肉好嚡。」有趣的是，安野只看得懂粵語口語文字，看不懂正規的書面語中文，我送過中文書給他，他坦言看不懂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人有自己的語言、自己的文字、自己的電影、自己的文化，連一個外國人都被上述語言、文字、電影、文化深深吸引，從零開始努力學習，香港人實在不應妄自菲薄，應該努力捍衛這一切才對，否則，我們的下一代就再也沒有機會接觸港式粵語與地道港產片了。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n<br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6Gv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9e7d3bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a>"},{"pid":"e3dd265723e2017414f86cc42af8262c4e0eda23","tid":659881,"uid":69568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接叫香港語 好似台語咁"},{"pid":"376c56d106e7c2fbcc96c4f4ce6d953d157233dd","tid":659881,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6acb4af0570595455df17e9142aa555a0eb1da32","tid":659881,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3dd265723e2017414f86cc42af8262c4e0eda23","tid":659881,"uid":69568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接叫香港語 好似台語咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"一早應該叫港語"},{"pid":"4d071cca75b3e31ac9ce0bfade909a3f6914def7","tid":659881,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6acb4af0570595455df17e9142aa555a0eb1da32","tid":659881,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3dd265723e2017414f86cc42af8262c4e0eda23","tid":659881,"uid":69568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接叫香港語 好似台語咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"一早應該叫港語"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"因為真係粵語 但過多幾年廣東省冇人識粵語之後就..."},{"pid":"0af97b701b45661be134415ab320ea6edcc1781f","tid":659881,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d071cca75b3e31ac9ce0bfade909a3f6914def7","tid":659881,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6acb4af0570595455df17e9142aa555a0eb1da32","tid":659881,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3dd265723e2017414f86cc42af8262